<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" type="notes">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="20997">Notes</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="20997">
Reported from Greece by 
<bibRefCitation author="Arvanitidis, Christos" journalOrPublisher="Bulletin of Marine Science" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" pagination="73 - 96" title="Polychaete fauna of the Aegean Sea: inventory and new information" volume="66" year="2000">Arvanitidis (2000a)</bibRefCitation>
. Type locality: Mediterranean (Gulf of Naples). Considered a synonym of 
<taxonomicName class="Polychaeta" family="Pectinariidae" genus="Lagis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Lagis koreni" order="Terebellida" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="koreni">Lagis koreni</taxonomicName>
Malmgren, 1866 by 
<bibRefCitation author="Fauvel, P." journalOrPublisher="Paul Lechevalier, Paris" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" title="Faune de France. Polychetes sedentaires" year="1927">Fauvel (1927)</bibRefCitation>
, thus it may have been overlooked in the area. 
<bibRefCitation author="Surugiu, V" journalOrPublisher="Lucrările Conferintei Nationale Biodiversitate si impact antropic in Marea Neagră si in ecosistemele litorale ale Mării Negre" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" pagination="47 - 56" title="New data on the polychaete fauna from the Romanian coast of the Black Sea" volume="Universitatea &quot; Al. I. Cuza &quot; Iasi" year="2006">Surugiu (2006)</bibRefCitation>
provides an overview of the differences between 
<taxonomicName class="Polychaeta" family="Pectinariidae" genus="Lagis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Lagis koreni" order="Terebellida" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="koreni">Lagis koreni</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName class="Polychaeta" family="Pectinariidae" genus="Lagis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Lagis neapolitana" order="Terebellida" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="neapolitana">Lagis neapolitana</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
